Package ezvcard.parameters

Class Summary
AddressTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the ADR and LABEL types.
CalscaleParameter Represents a CALSCALE parameter.
EmailTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the EMAIL type.
EncodingParameter Represents the "ENCODING" sub type.
ExpertiseLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the EXPERTISE property.
HobbyLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the HOBBY property.
ImageTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the PHOTO and LOGO types.
ImppTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the IMPP type.
InterestLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the INTEREST property.
KeyTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the KEY type.
LevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter.
MediaTypeParameter Represents a TYPE parameter that also has a media type associated with it.
RelatedTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the RELATED type.
SoundTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the SOUND type.
TelephoneTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the TEL type.
TypeParameter Represents a TYPE parameter.
ValueParameter Represents a VALUE parameter.
VCardParameter Represents a vCard parameter (aka "sub type") whose values are pre-defined.
